00:39:30.849 --> 00:39:34.407  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:53.81%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>you would welcome mine.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1322
00:39:34.407 --> 00:39:37.487  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:61.43%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Either way, it's up to you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1323
00:39:42.606 --> 00:39:49.164  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Well... it seems I won't</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1324
00:39:42.606 --> 00:39:49.164  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>be needing this anymore.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1325
00:39:59.979 --> 00:40:01.760  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:53.81%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>(</c.mono_sans></c.white><i><c.white><c.mono_sans> sighing contentedly )</c.mono_sans></c.white></i>

1326
00:40:05.439 --> 00:40:07.558  position:44.29%,start  align:start size:19.52%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>So...</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1327
00:40:07.558 --> 00:40:09.798  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:69.05%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>what shall we talk about first?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1328
00:40:25.913 --> 00:40:27.192  position:40.48%,start  align:start size:27.14%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Just you?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1329
00:40:27.192 --> 00:40:28.392  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:50.00%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I dropped my crew off</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1330
00:40:28.392 --> 00:40:30.111  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>at a Maquis base.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1331
00:40:30.111 --> 00:40:33.550  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:46.19%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I</c.mono_sans></c.white><i><c.white><c.mono_sans> had</c.mono_sans></c.white></i><c.white><c.mono_sans> to come back,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1332
00:40:30.111 --> 00:40:33.550  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:61.43%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>but I didn't see any reason</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1333
00:40:33.550 --> 00:40:36.190  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to drag them here</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1334
00:40:33.550 --> 00:40:36.190  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:69.05%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>just to face a prison sentence.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1335
00:40:36.190 --> 00:40:38.589  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:38.57%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You didn't have</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1336
00:40:36.190 --> 00:40:38.589  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:48.10%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to come back either.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1337
00:40:38.589 --> 00:40:42.108  position:38.57%,start  align:start size:30.95%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Yes. I did.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1338
00:40:42.108 --> 00:40:43.908  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>And I think we both know</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1339
00:40:43.908 --> 00:40:46.706  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:51.90%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>that's why you left us</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1340
00:40:43.908 --> 00:40:46.706  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>alone out there--</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1341
00:40:46.706 --> 00:40:49.346  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:44.29%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to see if I would.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1342
00:40:51.660 --> 00:40:54.944  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:61.43%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'm not going to stand here</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1343
00:40:51.660 --> 00:40:54.944  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:65.24%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>and apologize for what I did.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1344
00:40:54.944 --> 00:40:57.423  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:44.29%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You had your duty.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1345
00:40:57.423 --> 00:40:59.423  position:38.57%,start  align:start size:30.95%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I had mine.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1346
00:41:00.702 --> 00:41:02.981  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:50.00%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I still have my duty.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1347
00:41:04.181 --> 00:41:06.381  position:42.38%,start  align:start size:23.33%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I know.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1348
00:41:06.381 --> 00:41:09.619  position:40.48%,start  align:start size:29.05%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>And I know</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1349
00:41:06.381 --> 00:41:09.619  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:61.43%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'll probably go to prison.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1350
00:41:11.779 --> 00:41:15.538  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:67.14%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>But I came back because of us.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1351
00:41:15.538 --> 00:41:18.577  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:38.57%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Because despite</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1352
00:41:15.538 --> 00:41:18.577  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:48.10%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>all that's happened,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1353
00:41:18.577 --> 00:41:21.216  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:51.90%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I still love you, Ben.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1354
00:41:23.774 --> 00:41:25.615  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:70.95%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I don't want to throw that away.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1355
00:41:27.174 --> 00:41:28.414  position:42.38%,start  align:start size:23.33%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Do you?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1356
00:41:31.537 --> 00:41:32.533  position:46.19%,start  align:start size:15.71%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>No.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1357
00:41:59.804 --> 00:42:01.203  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Lieutenant Reese.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1358
00:42:08.762 --> 00:42:10.282  position:36.67%,start  align:start size:34.76%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'll be back.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1359
00:42:11.562 --> 00:42:12.920  position:44.29%,start  align:start size:34.76%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'll be here.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

